laboratory_examinations.findings: Opening pressure of 8 cm H2O and an extensive thoracic CSF leak.

laboratory_examinations.changes_over_time: Gradual resolution of the pachymeningeal enhancement noted on MRIs performed 6 and 12 months later.

laboratory_examinations.findings: 90% ipsilateral extracranial internal carotid artery stenosis.
Diffuse pachymeningeal enhancement and sagging of the brain.
Numerous large thoracic spinal meningeal diverticula.
